    <item>
      <title>Updated Female Dialogue Patch</title>
      <author>JuniperPlumdrop</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/606976</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/606976#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">c2f03c13cfb92ed1b008555a46bd33f650353165</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 07:41:56 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68757e78454c0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68757e784f4b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68757ff5668f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Updated Female Dialogue Patch&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed a broken line break in Baito's letter&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed an incorrect pronoun in Linda's dialogue after winning an auction&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;SariaOfTheKokiri made this excellent &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/50002"&gt;Female Dialogue Patch&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;However, there are some noted issues with it that they missed or changed erronously.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Users LilyArlatto, Yahtzeh, and Jameriquiah mentioned these errors that were missed by Saria. As Saria appears to have been inactive for a few years, I attempted to fix these myself.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I have also gone through and updated the opening crawl. In Saria's patch, the Hero of Time is referred to as a girl. I've changed this to refer to the Hero of Time as a "youth" so that the player can ascribe whatever gender they like to the Hero of Time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This patch is a modified version of the one used in &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/359761"&gt;Linkle Mod for Wind Waker HD&lt;/a&gt; by pokisofii. Therefore it should also still include the map icons from this mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;List of changes are as follows:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1) Pirates incorrectly referred to the player as "he" when sneaking into the bomb shop.&lt;br&gt;"I tell you, the minute I set my eyes on that [[player]], I just knew &lt;b&gt;he &lt;/b&gt;was hiding something back&amp;nbsp; at Outset, yeah?"&lt;br&gt;Updated "he" to "she"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2) When presenting the Cabana Deed to the butler door on the Private Oasis, it misses a space.&lt;br&gt;"Are you Mistress[[player]]?"&lt;br&gt;Added the space back in.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3) When beginning the Windfall trading sequence, there's a strange line break.&lt;br&gt;""Yes, yes! Young mistress, you are now my new salesman! No, no! Scratch that! Starting today, you and I are partners! Dear me, yes!""&lt;br&gt;Copied the original text back in and updated master to lady.&lt;br&gt;UPDATE 1.2: Formatting was still incorrect. Moved line breaks to resolve.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4) Odd line break in the letter with the IN-credible chart.&lt;br&gt;""To the esteemed Ms. Fairy-Person, Thank you very much for your purchase. Enclosed is an IN-credible Chart. This chart will show you where you can find the Triforce Charts. I want you to use it to find lots of them_they are my favorite kind of charts! And also, sir, have you been checking your Tingle Chart? Have you seen those giant fairy marks? Follow the chart to them and your fortune will increase greatly! Tingle""&lt;br&gt;Copied the original text back in and updated Mr. to Ms.&lt;br&gt;UPDATE 1.2: Formatting was still incorrect. Moved line breaks to resolve.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5) ""Hoy! You there! You Kingly Red Lion gal!"&lt;br&gt;Original patch incorrectly refers to the King of Red Lions as a 'gal'. Reverted 'gal' to 'guy'.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6) During the Pictograph sidequest, Lenzo incorrectly refers to the player as "his".&lt;br&gt;"And yet, [name], seeing as how you are one who has dedicated &lt;b&gt;his &lt;/b&gt;life to the art of photography, as I have..."&lt;br&gt;Updated "his" to "her"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;7) When talking to Ms. Marie when the pirates are on Windfall, she will say&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;"...What terrible weather we have today. Little boys shouldn't be out wandering around at a time like this! My, no!"&lt;br&gt;She's referring to the player with this text. Updated "boys" to "girls."&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;8) Opening crawl referring to the Hero of Time: Updated four instance of "girl" to "youth", and chaned "she" to "they". Now the Hero of Time's gender is indeterminate and the island's custom of garbing youths in green applies to all genders.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Update 1.1:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9) Updated the Master Sword description: "The legendary blade with the power&amp;nbsp;to repel evil...once wielded by the&amp;nbsp;legendary hero themself!"&lt;br&gt;Changed "himself/herself" to "themself"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10) Updated the Hero's Shield description: "This is the legendary shield said to&amp;nbsp;have been used by the hero themself!"&lt;br&gt;Changed "himself/herself" to "themself"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;11) Updated Fairy Fountain sign:&lt;br&gt;"This spot marks the remains of an ancient&amp;nbsp;Fairy Fountain. The legendary hero was said&amp;nbsp;to come here after battle so the fairies&amp;nbsp;could ease their weariness.&lt;br&gt;Updated "his/her weariness" to "their weariness".&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;12) Updated Tingle's letter containing the IN-credible chart:&lt;br&gt;"And also, miss, have you been checking your Tingle Chart?"&lt;br&gt;Updated "sir" to "miss".&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;13) Updated Tingle dialogue when you free him.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"Tingle knows without you telling him, ma'am! Yes, ma'am!"&lt;br&gt;For some reason in the original patch, the second "sir" was correctly updated to "ma'am" but the first was missed. Corrected this.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;14: Fixed a broken line break in Baito's letter:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="SelectedElement"&gt;"You're the woman, woman!"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Update 1.2: Made some pronouns gender neutral in reference to the Hero of Time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Update 1.3: Fixed a broken line break in Baito's letter&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Update 1.4: Corrected "she" to "he" in Linda's dialogue after winning the auction: "Well, honestly! Where on that tiny body could she be hiding all that cash?"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I've tested most of these changes personally, but there could still be some examples that I've missed. This is the final update for now.&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wwhd_updated_female_dialogue_patch.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
